cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CR, cs.MM, cs.LG 

The paper proposes a new methodology for iris recognition using deep learning-based image segmentation, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The focus of the paper is on post-mortem iris recognition, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR) and computer forensics (cs.CR). The paper also uses conventional iris recognition methods, which are related to multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG).
